snippet.title: CANDIED CAROLS: a romance visual novel based on the Nutcracker
snippet.description:
CANDIED CAROLS is a magical, wintry romance visual novel based on Tchaikovsky’s ballet, The Nutcracker.

Special thanks to YUniverse (http://www.youtube.com/c/YUniverse) for working with us to create this trailer!

FREE BETA RELEASE: 20 DECEMBER 2019

https://vi0let.itch.io/candied-carols 

4 routes:
FAE, The Sugar Plum Fairy: Ruka Samuels @ruka_samuels 
DIETRICH, The Rat King: Adam Carrizales @RatboyVA
JACK, The Nutcracker Prince: Joshua Waters @TunnelVa 
ALISTAIR, The Snow King: James Yamaguchi https://castingcall.club/m/Jyama 

Supporting characters:

MARZ, [Chocolate]: Kieran Flitton @KieranFlitton 
AZRA, [Coffee]: Sabrina Marie @k0torisan 
PEPPER & MINT [Candy Canes]: ao @chuunibyao 
TEMPO [Tea]: Alexander Hanly @Blairlexmydude
